Package de.fh.kiel.advancedjava.pojoapplication.rest.service

Class ClassHandlingService

java.lang.Object
de.fh.kiel.advancedjava.pojoapplication.rest.service.ClassHandlingService
@Service
public class ClassHandlingService
extends java.lang.Object
ClassHandlingService reads the relevant information from ASM ClassNodes and adds newly read Pojos to the database. For more information about ASM visit ASM
